summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Atlantic Street from Rainier Avenue to Sturgis Road, et al in the City of Seattle by constructing sewers and etc under Ordinance No. 17766, approved January 20, 1908, by creating Local Improvement District No.1688 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
